除"},{"pid":"c7af4250ed57b294bb1e2605b05da618488614f5","tid":830461,"uid":13059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"XR 變1080P 又成地精"},{"pid":"0aa668bf57beaeb2fde6955156bb6a37ef192822","tid":830461,"uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"不如擔心下and廠把啦"},{"pid":"4799804b5c8f6e85b2263ddf373ff10335364d91","tid":830461,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46014dd976d6faeab72bc3b0b7cd4081fdf4b966","tid":830461,"uid":9264,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c64d456ee25588740d825d9735bde27e64bae1bf","tid":830461,"uid":38805,"like":0,"dislike":64,"score":-64,"quote":{"pid":"f9831e319bbf41b9778f9b4b6c3e42931c5f1f0d","tid":830461,"uid":195438,"like":94,"dislike":4,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"又冇人話一年一定要換一個制程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三叔、GF、台積電個所謂7nm仲有排改進<br />\n玩多幾年都仲得<br />\n<br />\n而且，Apple只係負責設計電路<br />\n點樣突破7nm唔輪到佢地諗<br />\n等IBM同啲實驗室搞掂完再執佢地口水尾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"關IBM乜撚事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/aarontilley/2017/06/05/ibm-5nm-chips/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Faarontilley%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2Fibm-5nm-chips%2Famp%2F&d=rz%2B4S5xC%2F4d%2BlhhjbSBspb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=330fff32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/aarontilley/2017/06/05/ibm-5nm-chips/amp/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"台積電都會出5nm<br />\n要兩年後<br />\n所以下代iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pttnews.cc/d0abdaa26d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpttnews.cc%2Fd0abdaa26d&d=rz%2B4S5xC%2F4d%2BlhhjbSBspb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c1239acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://pttnews.cc/d0abdaa26d</a><br />\n<br />\n據DigiTimes援引台積電首席執行官魏哲家的話報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">5nm工藝需要等到2019年底或者2020年初才能實現大規模生產，試生產則會從2019年初開始。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　顯然蘋果想要在9月份或者10月份大規模鋪貨的話，A13處理器只好繼續採用7nm工藝。台積電CEO魏哲家還稱，公司預計將投資250億美元用於5nm技術投產，目前還沒有具體時間表。<br />\n<br />\n　　綜合來看，7nm工藝製式的芯片基本上已經可以滿足大多數用戶使用需求了，如果特別想嘗鮮5nm芯片的iPhone，不妨耐心等待2年吧。<br />\n<br />\n3nm又要隔2-3年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2018/08/16/tsmc-3nm-wafer-in-stsp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2Ftsmc-3nm-wafer-in-stsp%2F&d=rz%2B4S5xC%2F4d%2BlhhjbSBspb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=07a1be63\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2018/08/16/tsmc-3nm-wafer-in-stsp/</a><br />\n<br />\n台積電資深處長莊子壽指出，台積電 3 奈米總投資預估至少新台幣 6 千億元，若環評順利通過，預估 2020 年開始建廠，2021 年機器進場安裝，希望 2022 年底至 2023 年初開始量產。<br />\n<br />\n所以結論iphone都係要隔代買先算有突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6142091b33f055134974d5b6f24cfafe0a87a95","tid":830461,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"台積電5nm/***4nm頂三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7deb1517164e6b10b28910e6f3844233f2e5fe0","tid":830461,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"投資都要250億美金回唔回到本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfccb8b127460f9942a9e0b62b723c50a9412891","tid":830461,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"Apple又唔係未試過相同nm用兩年<br />\nA4同埋A5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877723